  "textPreview": "Free June 9 event: How to win brand visibility when AI decides what gets seen →\nSolutions\nTools\nResources\nPricing\nEN\nSign in\nRequest a demo\nStart free trial\nGoogle AI Mode Tracker\n\nSee how your brand appears in Google’s AI Mode, with one of the market’s first tools built specifically for it! Get the insights you need to boost your visibility in AI-driven search results that your audience is already relying on.\n\nStart free trial\nRequest a demo\n\nNo credit card required\n\nYour AI Mode performance at a glance\n\nBoost your content strategy with valuable data on your AI Mode appearance: know when you’re mentioned, which of your content gets cited the most, and see exactly which competitors are shown for keywords or prompts of your interest.\n\nTrack brand mentions and website links in AI Mode snippets\n\nSpot every mention of your brand or link to your website from Google’s AI Mode. Learn about your presence across key queries, even when your site isn’t directly linked.\n\nDiscover which of your content gets the most attention in AI Mode answers\n\nFind out which of your pages are most cited in AI responses. Use this insight to double down on high-performing content and identify what’s resonating most with AI answers.\n\nBenchmark your AI Mode presence against competitors\n\nTrack how often your competitors get featured in AI Mode snippets. See AI visibility distribution by business category, topic, and sub-topic. Find out which of your competitors’ content is used most often.\n\nSee the sources driving AI Mode answers\n\nFind domains and URLs Google pulls into AI Mode responses for your tracked prompts. Break down sources by type (media, blogs, forums) to understand what content formats Google favors\n\nTrack AI Mode visibility across the markets that matter to you\n\nMonitor performance across multiple countries and languages. Filter results by region and language to get locally relevant data.\n\nStart free trial\nTrack Google’s AI Mode with smart analytics\n1\nCheck how often your business appea",
